title: Biden's "Minor Incursion"
description: The fellas discuss foreign problems in Ukraine and domestic problems in schools before laughing about a New York Times deep dive into animal kingdom inequality. Rep. Billy Long from Missouri joins the progrum for an interview about his race for Senate.
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Comfortably Smug, Josh Holmes, Michael Duncan, John Ashbrook)
